1
00:00:57,640 --> 00:00:58,240
Bro.

2
00:01:00,880 --> 00:01:02,440
I ran into Qin's gang again.

3
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,680
Those guys came looking for trouble.

4
00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:05,680
We threw down a bit.

5
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:06,520
It's nothing.

6
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:11,120
I'm going after them.

7
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,840
Get back here.

8
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,240
Bro.

9
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,600
If we don't fight back hard,

10
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,080
they'll keep bullying us forever.

11
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:19,280
Sit down.

12
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:28,560
I can't take this anymore.

13
00:01:29,080 --> 00:01:30,320
Why do they get to make money?

14
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,320
Why do they get to buy houses?

15
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:32,800
While we have to live here,

16
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:33,920
eating rotten scraps.

17
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,200
Lin You.

18
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,640
Just hang in there.

19
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,200
One day, we'll get to live

20
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,080
that kind of life too.

21
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,400
If that day really comes,

22
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,960
I'm gonna live across the way.

23
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,360
Among all those skyscrapers,

24
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:53,000
one of them has to be ours.

25
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,720
And when that day comes,

26
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,080
nobody can bully us anymore.

27
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,120
Bro promises you,

28
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:01,560
that day will come for sure.

29
00:02:01,680 --> 00:02:02,640
And when it does,

30
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,920
it won't just be one house.

31
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,280
All those people who bullied us

32
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,480
all these years,

33
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,800
I'll knock every one of them down

34
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,520
and crush them under my feet.

35
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,600
By then,

36
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:16,840
the east side of the city is yours,

37
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,800
the west side is mine.

38
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,040
You be the General,

39
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:20,960
and I'll be your Vanguard.

40
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,120
Deal.

41
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,920
Whatever you say.

42
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,040
Don't worry, bro.

43
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:27,880
Leave it to me.

44
00:02:29,320 --> 00:02:29,720
Bro.

45
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,560
I learned a new move today.

46
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:33,920
Let's try it out.

47
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:34,680
Watch this.

48
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,240
Come on, take this!

49
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,960
Watch me! Watch me!

50
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:42,560
Here it comes!

51
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:43,960
And one more move...

52
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:46,160
Kamehameha!

53
00:02:48,040 --> 00:02:48,520
You lose!

54
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,280
That's no good.

55
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,360
You need real combat.

56
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,240
Watch this! Hey, what're you doing?

57
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,560
Come on, three, two, one!

58
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:56,720
You lose.

59
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,520
I lose, bro, I lose. You win, okay?

60
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:01,680
Bro.

61
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,320
Acting all cocky, huh?

62
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:04,880
Cocky, huh?

63
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,240
Get him!

64
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:08,800
Cocky!

65
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,360
Hit him!

66
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:12,640
Big bro!

67
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,520
Lin You!

68
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,600
The cops are here, run!

69
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:29,880
Don't be scared.

70
00:03:30,920 --> 00:03:31,400
Lin You.

71
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,200
I'm fine.

72
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,280
Bro's got you.

73
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:36,840
Don't be scared, don't be scared.

74
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:37,600
Bro's right here.

75
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,160
Lin You.

76
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:49,760
You think this is one of your comics?

77
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,960
Ghosts and spirits belong in comics.

78
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,920
How could there be ghosts in real life?

79
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:55,280
You're just...

80
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,280
You're as stubborn as an ox.

81
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,800
You grabbed onto their boss

82
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:00,360
and called him a dead man.

83
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:03,200
Now we've got no room to maneuver at all.

84
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:04,440
You... you...

85
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:05,640
Unbelievable.

86
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:08,080
You can't even tell reality from comics.

87
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,240
Lin You.

88
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,200
Did you know

89
00:04:11,600 --> 00:04:12,680
Qin Jianping before?

90
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,880
Even if he did, he...

91
00:04:14,880 --> 00:04:15,680
Excuse me,

92
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,279
is this the Daji Agency?

93
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,160
Blessings of the Infinite Lord.

94
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,560
How can I help you?

95
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:21,839
Mr. Lin You.

96
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,280
Your brother sent me to bring you to him.

97
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,920
Brother?

98
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:27,640
You...

99
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,400
You have a brother? How did I not know?

100
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:32,960
Mr. Wu Qianchen, chairman of Dingfeng Group,

101
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,200
is our boss.

102
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,040
Oh, and Mr. Wang,

103
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,360
the money you owed Jianping's company,

104
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,600
our boss has already paid it off for you.

105
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,800
Paid off?

106
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,640
Lin You, this...

107
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,920
Lin You!

108
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,400
Your brother's something else!

109
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:50,600
Your brother's a real stand-up guy.

110
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,680
He paid it all off!

111
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,360
All of it!

112
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,600
Well...

113
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:55,880
go on, then.

114
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,680
Go, go, go!

115
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:17,880
Bro.

116
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,560
What are you standing there for?

117
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,320
Come, have some tea.

118
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,120
Ever since you got out,

119
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,080
you've grown pretty distant from me.

120
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,520
You don't come to me with anything anymore.

121
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,880
Didn't we agree

122
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,720
that once we had our turf,

123
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,000
the East side would be mine

124
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,120
and the West side would be yours?

125
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,200
Now we've got the turf,

126
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,960
but you won't come back.

127
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:08,280
I don't want that old life anymore.

128
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:11,280
I just want to live like an ordinary person.

129
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,480
An ordinary person?

130
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,160
Playing a Taoist to swindle and bluff?

131
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:20,160
Or selling houses at an agency?

132
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,080
I'll stop teasing you.

133
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:28,600
Let's deal with business first.

134
00:06:38,960 --> 00:06:39,480
Bro,

135
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,960
why is he here with you?

136
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,720
Wasn't he already dead?

137
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:54,960
He's not dead.

138
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:57,080
He just got lucky.

139
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,400
But back in prison,

140
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,360
I heard that he was definitely dead.

141
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,200
That's why I felt so much regret.

142
00:07:08,080 --> 00:07:10,400
You knew he was alive all along, didn't you?

143
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:13,240
Why didn't you tell me?

144
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,320
Why?

145
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,960
No wonder every time I visited you,

146
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,360
you kept bringing him up.

147
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,480
I only found out later that he wasn't dead.

148
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:29,760
Lin You,

149
00:07:31,120 --> 00:07:33,120
do you know why I've kept him alive

150
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,240
all these years?

151
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,120
Stab him.

152
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,800
Boss Wu,

153
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,320
is this what you wanted me to do?

154
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,920
I remember back then, the stab was...

155
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,600
right here.

156
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:20,840
No, wait.

157
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:23,000
Here.

158
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,880
Stab him.

159
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,600
Are you insane?

160
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,080
Old Qin.

161
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,840
What needs to be done,

162
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,240
you know full well.

163
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,600
The cops will be here soon.

164
00:09:28,560 --> 00:09:29,840
What you've done these past few years,

165
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,920
and how to explain it,

166
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:32,960
you know exactly what to say.

167
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:36,200
As for the ten years you owe my brother,

168
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,640
let's call it paid.

169
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:50,920
Old Qin.

170
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,120
Don't worry.

171
00:09:54,320 --> 00:09:55,360
Your family,

172
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,960
I'll take good care of them for you.

173
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,760
Boss Wu.

174
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,080
I hope you're a man of your word.

175
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,000
Where are you going?

176
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:33,000
Back to my old life.

177
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:44,360
I've seen how powerful you are,

178
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,480
Boss Wu.

179
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:49,240
That's exactly why you should stay here.

180
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,240
I'm the only family you have.

181
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,080
I'm the only one who can protect you.

182
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,800
You're insane. Insane.

183
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:13,040
Brother Chen.

184
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,880
Want me to go bring Brother You back?

185
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,440
You can't stop him.

186
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,240
He'll come back on his own.

187
00:12:06,160 --> 00:12:07,040
What's the meaning of this?

188
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:08,880
Did Wu Qianchen put you up to this?

189
00:12:09,640 --> 00:12:10,800
Say something!

190
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,800
What are you trying to do?
